Pre-dispersed organo-montmorillonite (organo-MMT) nanofiller: Morphology, 
cytocompatibility and impact on flexibility, toughness and biostability of 
biomedical ethyl vinyl acetate (EVA) copolymer.

Osman AF(1), M Fitri TF(2), Rakibuddin M(3), Hashim F(4), Tuan Johari SAT(5), 
Ananthakrishnan R(3), Ramli R(6).

Author information:
(1)Center of Excellence Geopolymer and Green Technology (CEGeoGTech), School of 
Materials Engineering, University Malaysia Perlis, 02600, Perlis, Malaysia. 
Electronic address: azlin@unimap.edu.my.
(2)Center of Excellence Geopolymer and Green Technology (CEGeoGTech), School of 
Materials Engineering, University Malaysia Perlis, 02600, Perlis, Malaysia.
(3)Department of Chemistry, Indian Institute of Technology Kharagpur, India.
