Cardiac iron overload in chronically transfused patients with thalassemia, 
sickle cell anemia, or myelodysplastic syndrome.

de Montalembert M(1)(2), Ribeil JA(3)(4), Brousse V(1)(2), Guerci-Bresler A(5), 
Stamatoullas A(6), Vannier JP(7), Dumesnil C(7), Lahary A(8), Touati M(9), 
