Klinefelter syndrome: cardiovascular abnormalities and metabolic disorders.

Calogero AE(1), Giagulli VA(2), Mongioì LM(3), Triggiani V(4), Radicioni AF(5), 
Jannini EA(6), Pasquali D(7); Klinefelter ItaliaN Group (KING).

